OL,3,CNigel Farage denies Reform promised
OL,4,Ccouncil tax cuts despite leaflet pledge
OL,6,FNigel Farage has denied Reform UK
OL,7,Fpromised to cut council tax in Kent,
OL,8,Fdespite an election leaflet pledging
OL,9,Fto "reduce waste and cut your taxes".
OL,11,FThe Reform-run Kent County Council
OL,12,Frecently voted to increase council tax
OL,13,Fby 3.99%, below the annual maximum of
OL,14,F5%.
OL,16,FThe party leader insisted they were
OL,17,F"putting up council tax less than the
OL,18,Fother parties where they control
OL,19,Fcouncils" and denied they had ever
OL,20,Fcommitted to lower bills.
OL,26,@qD@DOUqD@dO]yD@AOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
