OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773155490
OL,3,CNigel Farage denies Reform promised
OL,4,Ccouncil tax cuts despite leaflet pledge
OL,6,FBut a flyer from last year's local
OL,7,Felections ` in which the party swept
OL,8,Fto a landslide victory at County Hall
OL,9,Fin Maidstone ` called on voters to
OL,10,F"change the way Kent County Council
OL,11,Fspend your money" and said the party
OL,12,Fwould "reduce waste and cut your
OL,13,Ftaxes".
OL,15,FMr Farage told ITV News Meridian: "We
OL,16,Fdid not say we'd cut tax."
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@QO]tD@GOUuD@FO]wD@cOUxD@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
