OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773155490
OL,3,CNigel Farage denies Reform promised
OL,4,Ccouncil tax cuts despite leaflet pledge
OL,6,FWhen challenged about the wording of
OL,7,Fthe Kent leaflet, the Reform UK leader
OL,8,Fsaid: "Well, cutting taxes could mean
OL,9,Fnot putting them up as much, I
OL,10,Fsuppose. But I never promised cuts in
OL,11,Fcouncil tax."
OL,13,FResponding to the interview, the
OL,14,FLabour MP for Chatham and Aylesford,
OL,15,FTris Osborne, said: "They promised to
OL,16,Fcut taxes and to implement DOGE-style
OL,17,Fsavings to local taxpayers.
OL,26,@pD@GOUsD@MO]wD@UOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
