PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773155490
OL,3,CNigel Farage denies Reform promised
OL,4,Ccouncil tax cuts despite leaflet pledge
OL,6,F"They raised taxes and delivered no
OL,7,Fsavings that weren't already planned.
OL,8,FNigel has already moved on. Sadly left
OL,9,Fthe consequences for our residents."
OL,11,FWhen the county council approved the
OL,12,Ftax rise in February, the Labour
OL,13,Fleader of Medway Council, Vince Maple,
OL,14,Fposted a picture of the election
OL,15,Fleaflet on social media with the
OL,16,Fcaption: "Election promise broken
OL,17,Ftoday by Reform in Kent."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@dO]xD@JOUyD@YO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
