OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773155490
OL,3,CNigel Farage denies Reform promised
OL,4,Ccouncil tax cuts despite leaflet pledge
OL,6,FA Reform UK spokesperson told ITV
OL,7,FNews: "Our literature has been
OL,8,Fwilfully misinterpreted by the Tories,
OL,9,Fwho despite explicitly pledging to
OL,10,Flower council tax in May are now
OL,11,Fraising tax to the max in the councils
OL,12,Fthey won, and Labour who have imposed
OL,13,Fthe highest tax burden on this country
OL,14,Fin its history.
OL,16,FThe spokesperson added: "Wherever
OL,17,FReform took control we have rooted out
OL,18,Fwaste and kept taxes low, with Reform
OL,19,Fcouncils on average boasting far lower
OL,20,Fcouncil tax rises than any other party.
OL,26,@oD@GOUxD@YOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
