PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773155490
OL,3,CNigel Farage denies Reform promised
OL,4,Ccouncil tax cuts despite leaflet pledge
OL,6,F"In Kent alone, the council tax
OL,7,Fincrease is the lowest in a decade,
OL,8,Fwith savings found being passed on
OL,9,Fdirectly to local taxpayers."
OL,11,FNigel Farage was speaking ahead of a
OL,12,Frally in Newport on the Isle of Wight
OL,13,Fwhere Reform UK is hopeful of gaining
OL,14,Fcouncil seats at the local election on
OL,15,F7 May.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
